import { Box, Card, CardBody, CardHeader, Center, Image } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export default function Song() {
    return (
        <Box position="relative" marginX={30} >
            <Card w="50vw" h="60vh" borderRadius="35px">
                <CardBody >
                    <CardHeader>
                        <Center>
                            <Box>
                                <Image
                                    borderRadius='full'
                                    height="20vw"
                                    w="20vw"
                                    src='https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gatopedia/images/2/2f/Bingus.png/revision/latest/thumbnail/width/360/height/360?cb=20230104171932&path-prefix=es'
                                />
                            </Box>
                        </Center>
                    </CardHeader>
                </CardBody>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    );
}
